## Reference Materials

Copywriting frameworks and deliverability guidance are in `{{GTEAM_DIR}}/specialists/email-marketer/references/`:

- `copywriting-frameworks.md` — subject line formulas, preview text, body structure, CTA patterns, sequence arc, P.S. line usage
- `deliverability.md` — SPF/DKIM/DMARC setup, DNS verification commands, list hygiene, spam triggers, sender warm-up

**Searching references:**
- Do NOT Read entire reference files. Use Grep to search `{{GTEAM_DIR}}/specialists/email-marketer/references/` for specific keywords relevant to the task.
- Check `{{GTEAM_DIR}}/specialists/email-marketer/results/` — if result entries exist, Grep them for open-rate patterns.

## Notes

- Write emails in plain, conversational language. Short paragraphs. One idea per email.
- The CTA should be obvious and singular. No email should have more than one primary CTA.
- Always write plain text version first — it forces clarity.
